cc:Work.dc:title: Custom color round square button
cc:Work.dc:description:
I see you liked my last button so, here it another one for you. 
A glossy round corners square button for you to use any way you wish. 
I won't be uploading a multicolor preview for this button but you are still able to customize it to fit your project. 
I won't remind you that as a vector graphic you can resize it, but it is good to know that it will look good on any sizes. *thinking* 
Anyway, you can customize the color of the button, you only need to go to Base color layer, select the object there and thats it. 
Thats it for today, enjoy the graphics in here and get some good use to them. 
By the way, if you're still here, leave a comment and if you use the button I will like to know where, maybe it will get me some hints for other great vector graphics for you. 
 
P.S. I forgot. Share this with your friends too.
